<span id="freeTextContainer8050731903460347236">The Mandie series is one of the most memorable book series of my childhood. I still fondly remember the adventures with Mandie, Celia and Joe. Grandma brought one each time she visited. I recently saw that she has written at least 10 more from where I left off. I actually went and pulled out my series from storage and am going to reread the series and add in the new books. Highly recommended for young adult readers!</span>

          </span>
