        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer101640523" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11316295486221973382">I thought that as the Mandie books went on they got a little boreing and not as good as the first. My favorites are the first three. Its seems that Mandie is always getting into trouble in this book, and it gets old. But otherwise, Mandie books are the best! </span>

          </span>
        </div>


